      },
      "startTime": 6.2999999523,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_bar-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "bar-00-night",
      "startTime": 8.5666670959
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_03_03-kan002.m4a",
      "text": "kanaは大人だから～とか考えずに、好きだなって\n思ったら、自分の気持ちに素直に行動しますね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Since kana is an adult~ When I feel something‚\nI try to act honestly with my emotions.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 12.266667064,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_bar-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "bar-00-night",
      "startTime": 16.7333335083
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_bar-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "bar-00-night",
      "startTime": 21.7333334764
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_03_03-kan003.m4a",
      "text": "恋愛観ですか？　そうですね……\nいい人がいれば、自分に嘘はつきたくないです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "As for my views on love?\nWell… If I like someone‚ I don't want to lie.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 21.7333334764,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_03_03-kan004.m4a",
      "text": "でも今は、恋愛していなくてもファンのみなさんに\n囲まれて、アイドルでいられることが幸せですし",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But even if I'm not in a relationship right now‚ being surrounded\nby fans and being able to be an idol is happiness.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 29.4535529856,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_bar-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "bar-00-night",
      "startTime": 33.7666668416
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_03_03-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "（さすがに本番になると）\n（読者層にあわせてしっかり語るんだな）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（As expected‚ when it comes back to her main job）\n（She knows how to speak well according to the audience.）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 35.8666668098,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_bar-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "bar-00-night",
      "startTime": 39.3333335083
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_03_03-kan005.m4a",
      "text": "――読者からの質問ですか？\nんー……好きな人の前で素が見せられない",
      "translations": {
        "en": "――Is this a question from a reader?\nHmm~… I think it's unnecessary to forcibly show your true feelings",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 42.3000001431,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_bar-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "bar-00-night",
      "startTime": 48.0666676045
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_03_03-kan006.m4a",
      "text": "別に無理に見せる必要はないと思いますよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "in front of someone you like.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 48.0666676045,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_bar-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "bar-00-night",
      "startTime": 52.2666698933
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_03_03-kan007.m4a",
      "text": "素のままでいて、それでもずーっと愛される人なんて\n滅多にいないんじゃないかな？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Even if it's the true self‚ I wonder if there are hardly any people\nwho continue to be loved.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 56.5333365281,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_03_03-kan008.m4a",
      "text": "好きな人には可愛く思われたい！　って\n自分を取り繕っちゃう気持ち、kanaも分かります～",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Wanting to be cute in front of someone you like!\nkana understand that feeling of wanting tp imitate ~",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 61.9666698615,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_bar-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "bar-00-night",
      "startTime": 66.3000032266
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
