      "text": "きっと相手もそう思ってるから\n悩む必要はないんじゃないですか",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Surely the other person would think the same‚\nso there's no need to worry‚ right?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 74.4000031948,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_03_03-kan011.m4a",
      "text": "それに、素ってさ、隠しているつもりでも心を許した\n人には、勝手に見せてしまっているものだと思いますし",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Besides‚ even if you try to hide your true feelings‚\nit seems like they naturally show to the people you allow into your heart.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 83.0000031948,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_bar-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "bar-00-night",
      "startTime": 87.4000032266
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
