      "translations": {
        "en": "What? Spit it out.\nI'm in a good mood‚ so I'll answer.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 126.6666678269,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_03_03-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "さっきのインタビューって\nまさか実体験に基づいてたりしませんよね……？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "About the interview earlier…\nIt wasn't based on actual experiences‚ was it…?",
