      },
      "startTime": 131.9235285133,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_03_03-kan016.m4a",
      "text": "はぁ！？　な、何言ってんの！　同年代の支持を\n得るために作ってきたって言ったっしょ！！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Huh!? W-what are you saying?!\nI said it was made to gain support from our peers!!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 141.9333405971,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_03_03-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "それならいいんです\nでも、あまりにも具体的だったので",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That's fine then.\nBut it was so specific that…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 146.8914922661,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_03_03-kan017.m4a",
      "text": "おい、kanaのことナメてんの？\nあれくらいいつもやってるから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hey‚ are you underestimating me?\nI always do stuff like that.",
        "id": ""
      },
