      "text": "いえ……先日恋愛解禁だ～と言っていたので\n恋人が出来たとか勘ぐってしまって……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "No… Since you said \"love ban is lifted~\" the other day‚\nI thought you might have gotten a boyfriend…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 165.9333578903,
      "sfxList": []
